  "description": "Discover better ores and find higher quality minerals while you're mining, thanks to the glowing ore vein indicator.",
  "body": "## 🎮 Better Ore – Resource Pack for Minecraft\n🔍 Main Function: Better Ore is a resource pack designed to make finding ores in caves and the Nether easier. Using bright outlines, it makes ores much more visible during exploration and mining.\n\n### 🪨 Highlighted Ores:\n- In the Overworld: Coal, Iron, Copper, Lapis Lazuli, Redstone, Gold, Diamond, Emerald\n- In the Nether: Nether Quartz, Netherite, Ancient Debris\n\n### 🌍 Compatibility:\n- Compatible with all dimensions (Overworld, Nether)\n- Compatible with recent versions of Minecraft\n\n**🛠️ Creator:** Developed by Cobble Studio, a studio specializing in creating visual and technical solutions to enhance the Minecraft player experience.",
